# **3️⃣ README.md Draft (Project 1 – Fullstack Authentication App)**

```markdown
# Fullstack Authentication App

A complete login & signup system using React.js, Node.js, Express, and MongoDB.

## 🚀 Purpose
This project demonstrates a full-stack authentication system with JWT-based login and signup. Users can register, login, and access protected routes.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Frontend: React.js, Bootstrap
- Backend: Node.js, Express.js
- Database: MongoDB
- Authentication: JWT (JSON Web Tokens)

## ⚡ Features
- User Signup & Login
- JWT Authentication & Protected Routes
- Responsive UI
- Clean Code with comments

## 📂 Installation

### Backend
```bash
cd backend
npm install
# create .env file with keys
npm run dev
